javax.jnlp
Interface ServiceManagerStub

public interface ServiceManagerStub

A ServiceManagerStub object implements the particular lookup of JNLP services by the JNLP Client. The object is registered with the ServiceManager using the ServiceManager.setServiceManagerStub(javax.jnlp.ServiceManagerStub) method.

1.0
